## Cleaning

Just removing first two columns and making dates actual date types. 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
lubbock_clean <- lubbock |> select( 
  -"1",
  -"2"
) |> mutate(
  date_arrest = ymd(date_arrest),
  date_released = ymd(date_released)
)
```
